name: The Death of a Star
description:
This atmospheric picture taken with the NASA/ESA Hubble Space Telescope, shows a dark, gloomy scene in the constellation of Gemini (The Twins).

Name:	NGC 2371
Type:	Milky Way : Nebula : Type : Planetary
Constellation:	Gemini
